results.name: Black Castlerock Grey
results.title: New Balance 9060 Black Castlerock Grey
results.description:
The New Balance 9060 Black Castlerock Grey was inspired by a 90s model and comes in a grey, black, and red colorway.

This Black New Balance 9060 sneaker consists of a black mesh base with monochromatic pigskin suede and leather overlays. The shoe is designed with "N" branding on the side panel, a plush tongue, and flat laces. The model has a CR device at the heel. The design is completed by a chunky, dual-density midsole equipped with ABZORB and SBS cushioning.

The New Balance 9060 Black Castlerock Grey was released on September 2nd, 2022, at a retail price of $150.

results.name: Rain Cloud Grey
results.title: New Balance 9060 Rain Cloud Grey
results.description:
The New Balance 9060 Rain Cloud Grey takes on an early 2000s design by the American brand.

The sneaker displays tones of grey and off-white. It features a mixed-material upper that combines pigskin suede overlays with mesh, and the "N" emblem is accented with multiple silver details. The medial logo has a deconstructed appearance made up of parallel lines, while the"N" is solid on the lateral. The dual-density midsole, which sits on top of the diamond-shaped outsole, combines SBS cushioning and ABZORB technology.

The New Balance 9060 Rain Cloud Grey debuted on September 2nd, 2022, and originally retailed at $150.

results.name: White Silver Navy
results.title: New Balance 530 White Silver Navy
results.description:
The New Balance 530 White Silver Navy features a white mesh upper with metallic silver and white leather overlays. On the quarter panel, a grey New Balance logo outlined in navy adds contrast. From there, a white and grey ABZORB sole adds the finishing touch.

The New Balance 530 White Silver Navy released in February of 2021 and retailed for $95.

results.name: Silver Classic Crimson
results.title: New Balance 1906R Silver Classic Crimson
results.description:
The New Balance 1906R Silver Classic Crimson is a colorway of the 2000s-inspired running shoe containing cushioning technology.

This version of the New Balance 1906R is made with a lightweight white upper. Synthetic overlays in silver with Classic Crimson accents cross the entire upper, from the toebox to the laces, across the midsole, and back to the heel. The midsole also features a black mesh panel. The New Balance N appears on both sides of the shoe in crimson, white, and silver with N-Lock branding in the middle. The heel is supported by a silver TPU cage that has an NB logo on it, and three red stripes are found above it. The tongue also sports a logo patch.

What we like most about this shoe is the ACTEVA LITE, N-ergy, and ABZORB cushioning in the midsole, sole, and outsole that all work together to make this shoe extra comfortable. The New Balance 1906R Silver Classic Crimson was released on November 16, 2023, for a price of $155.

results.name: Protection Pack Rain Cloud
results.title: New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Rain Cloud
results.description:
The New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Rain Cloud features a grey mesh upper with tonal jagged suede overlays and a reflective New Balance logo. From there, a cream Nrgy midsole and grey outsole complete the design.

The New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Rain Cloud released in August of 2021 and retailed for $150.

results.name: Silver Metallic Blue Agate
results.title: New Balance 1906R Silver Metallic Blue Agate
results.description:
Meet the New Balance 1906R Silver Metallic Blue Agate, a fresh iteration of the much-lauded 1906R model. Released on December 8, 2023, this sneaker quickly captured the attention of the masses with its unique blend of retro design and contemporary aesthetics. Featuring a sleek silver metallic hue complemented by blue agate accents, this sneaker is a testament to New Balance's commitment to innovation and style.

The New Balance 1906R has garnered immense popularity for its exceptional comfort and suave design, and the Silver Metallic Blue Agate colorway is no exception. It stands out with its sea salt touches that enhance the metallic and blue agate tones, embodying a sense of sophistication and modernity. The sneaker's silhouette is a nod to New Balance's rich heritage while propelling the brand into the forefront of trendy fashion.

Available for $155, the New Balance 1906R Silver Metallic Blue Agate is a true statement piece. Its launch was not merely a release but an event that underscored the resurgence of classic sneaker profiles in today's fashion landscape. Whether paired with casual wear or as a complement to a more dressed-up look, these kicks are versatile, stylish, and an embodiment of New Balance's distinguished craftsmanship and forward-thinking design.

results.name: Protection Pack Phantom
results.title: New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Phantom
results.description:
The New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Phantom features a charcoal mesh upper with monotone jagged suede overlays and unfinished edges. From there, a black Nrgy midsole and matching outsole add the finishing touches.

The New Balance 2002R Protectioon Pack Phantom released in August of 2021 and retailed for $150.

results.name: White Green
results.title: New Balance 550 White Green
results.description:
The New Balance 550 White Green features a smooth white leather upper with a grey suede toe wrap and green detailing. From there, a New Balance Basketball woven tongue label and matching sole completes the design.

The New Balance 550 White Green released in June of 2021 and retailed for $120.

results.name: White Metallic Gold
results.title: New Balance 1906R White Metallic Gold
results.description:
The New Balance 1906R White Metallic Gold comes in a metallic silver and metallic gold color scheme.

The New Balance 1906R White Metallic Gold adopts a classic silhouette with white leather and gold embellishments. The upper is breathable and lightweight, with a cushioned collar and tongue for comfort. The midsole is constructed from lightweight EVA foam for cushioning and support. Durable rubber is used to construct the outsole, which provides grip and steadiness. The shoe also features "N" branding in a contrasting gold and black colorway on both lateral sides.

The New Balance 1906R White Metallic Gold was made available on August 12th, 2022, for a retail price of $155.

results.name: White Silver Metallic
results.title: New Balance 530 White Silver Metallic
results.description:
The New Balance 530 White Silver Metallic is a sneaker that was released in a retro-silhouette as part of the New Balance 530 collection.

Featuring a predominately white colorway with silver metallic accents, the Balance 530 White Silver Metallic includes a predominantly mesh construction. The shoe features a cushioned midsole that provides excellent support and impact resistance. In addition, the shoe has a rubber outsole, which offers excellent traction and grip. Moreover, the sneaker also has a low-laying collar that is padded and a pull tag on the heel. The tongue is padded as well and is finished off with a New Balance running logo. The 530 label can also be seen on the side.

We think that one of the standout features of the New Balance 530 White Silver Metallic is the leather overlay that is designed to encase the mesh structure. The shoe was released on January 4th, 2023, at a retail price of $100.

results.name: Marblehead Light Aluminum
results.title: New Balance 2002R Marblehead Light Aluminum
results.description:
The New Balance 2002R Marblehead Light Aluminum was originally released in 2005. Its minimalist features shades of grey colorway.

The stylish and versatile New Balance 2002R Marblehead Light Aluminum top features several colors of grey. Its design is of the platinum fabric base and supple leather details. It consists of a netting top with a plain, perforated ashy faux leather surface. It also displays a matching outsole that complements the finishing. The New Balance 2002R Marblehead Light Aluminum has ABZORB innovation and N-ergy padding underfoot.

The New Balance 2002R Marblehead Light Aluminum was released in September of 2020 for a price of $140.

results.name: Silver Cream
results.title: New Balance 530 Silver Cream
results.description:
The New Balance 530 Silver Cream was released in celebration of the brands 30th anniversary.

This model has a cream-toned mesh base with silver and grey synthetic overlays. The "N" logos on the shoe quarters also comes in a silver hue with a black outline. Further branding includes the "NB" text on its padded tongue, also in a silver tone, and a 530 text on the shoe collar. The base is equipped with an ABZORB midsole that provides light cushioning, and completes its design.

The New Balance 530 Silver Cream was released on the market on January 7th, 2023. It retailed at a price of $100.

results.name: Steel Grey Orca
results.title: New Balance 2002R Steel Grey Orca
results.description:
The New Balance 2002R Steel Grey Orca is an iteration of the New Balance 2002R running sneaker in a Steel Grey Orca colorway.

This sneakers upper is made of a Grey mesh base cut out by Steel and Lead Grey leather overlays on the toe box. Lead Grey accents also appear on the upper eyelets, quarter panel, and the upper part of the tongue. The top overlay, which dominates the upper, features a premium Suede build in a Steel Grey tone highlighted by a Light Grey N logo with a White outline and 2002R branding on the lateral ankle. A White Absorb midsole and a Black N-ergy outsole round out the design.

The New Balance 2002R Steel Grey Orca White was made available on October 21st, 2022, retailing at $140.

results.name: Sea Salt White
results.title: New Balance 9060 Sea Salt White
results.description: The New Balance 9060 Sea Salt White is a sleek and stylish sneaker that combines modern design with classic elements. The upper is made of premium leather and mesh, providing durability and breathability. The sea salt white colorway gives the shoe a clean and minimalist look, making it a versatile addition to any wardrobe. The release date for this shoe is January 14th, 2023, and with a retail price of $150. The New Balance 9060 Sea Salt White is perfect for those who want a comfortable and fashionable sneaker that can be worn for any occasion. With its high-quality materials and attention to detail, this shoe is sure to impress.

results.name: White Black
results.title: New Balance 550 White Black
results.description:
Taking cues from the 1989 New Balance P550, the New Balance 550 White Black features a smooth white leather upper with perforated overlays and black piping. Puffed New Balance logos decorate the quarter panel. At the base, a matching white and black sole completes the design.

The New Balance 550 White Black released in November of 2021 and retailed for $110.

results.name: Granite Pink
results.title: New Balance 9060 Granite Pink
results.description:
The New Balance 9060 Granite Pink finds inspiration in the visible tech aesthetic found in running shoes from the early 2000s.

The upper is crafted from breathable mesh in Pink Granite with pig suede and leather overlays in Granite. The New Balance "N" on the outer side panel is made of synthetic leather in metallic silver, while the "N" on the inner side panel is made up of reflective tape lines. The sculpted midsole houses ABZORB and SBS cushioning, which protects against impact and adds a bulky aesthetic to this 2000s-inspired sneaker. The front lace-up closure is adjustable and houses off-white laces that match the technical midsole pods.

Our experts at StockX like the subtle branding details, including the tongues logo tag and the "new balance" lettering on the synthetic insole. The New Balance 9060 Granite Pink was released on February 15, 2024, and retailed at $150.

results.name: Action Bronson Medusa Azul
results.title: New Balance 1906R Action Bronson Medusa Azul
results.description:
Created as part of American rapper Action Bronsons second series with New Balance, the New Balance 1906R Action Bronson Medusa Azul adds cool blue tones and rich earthy hues to the recognizable 1906R silhouette.

While the Action Bronson Medusa Azul New Balance 1906R boasts all the technical features associated with the 1906R, including segmented ABZORB SBS pods beneath the heel and flexible cushioning in the midsole, the "Medusa Azul" colorway makes it stand out from other models. The upper construction features light blue mesh as the base, golden brown mesh below the N logo, and synthetic overlays in light grayish purple. Co-branding details decorate the tongue, the insole, and the silicone hangtag, while durable boot laces secure the front closure system.

Our experts at StockX like the colorblocking on the midsole and outsole, which highlights the ABZORB SBS pods and other technical features. The New Balance 1906R Action Bronson Medusa Azul was released on June 21, 2024, and retailed at $185.

results.name: White Grey
results.title: New Balance 550 White Grey
results.description:
The New Balance 550 White Grey features a white leather upper with monochromatic perforated leather overlays and puffed New Balance logos. From there, a woven New Balance Basketball tongue label and matching sole completes the design.

The New Balance 550 White Grey released in June of 2021 and retailed for $100.

results.name: Raincloud
results.title: New Balance 530 Raincloud
results.description:
The New Balance 530 Raincloud continues the legacy of the original 530 which debuted in 1992. The "Raincloud" takes the performance sneakers bulky silhouette and adds a grey-tone color scheme.

The Raincloud, Grey, and White colorway is inspired by the hue of a raincloud just before it pours and is similar to the color scheme found on several New Balance 990s. The sneaker features a breathable mesh upper with soft suede overlays in a complementing grey. The New Balance N graces the side panel, while 530 can be found next to the heel overlay. The bulky ABZORB midsole gives the sneaker a 90s look and cushions against impact. The rubber outsole provides traction that grips the ground without decreasing flexibility. The "Raincloud" also comes with a padded tongue and collar, which add extra comfort.

Something our StockX experts love is the way the white midsole contrasts the small, black outsole. The New Balance 530 Raincloud was released on June 9, 2023, and retailed at $100.

results.name: Magnet
results.title: New Balance 9060 Magnet
results.description:
The New Balance 9060 Magnet represents a fresh interpretation of the refined style and innovation-driven design found in the classic 99X series.

With a magnet colorway accented by shades of gray, the New Balance 9060 showcases a modern and streamlined aesthetic. Its contemporary appeal is emphasized by suede overlays and a mesh upper, coupled with flat cotton laces and TPU eyelets. Drawing influence from the 990, the 9060 Magnet incorporates sway bars across the entire upper, creating a visually dynamic effect. Wavy lines and exaggerated proportions on a sculpted pod midsole enhance the familiar cushioning technologies of ABZORB and SBS. Inspired by the original 991 lace jewel, the tongue logo adds a distinctive touch, while the diamond outsole pattern, borrowed from the classic 860, completes the overall design.

The standout characteristic of the New Balance 9060 Magnet lies in its advanced cushioning technology. Featuring ABZORB and SBS technologies in the sole, the shoe delivers dynamic and lightweight cushioning for optimal comfort and performance. The sneaker debuted for $150 on September 25th, 2023.

results.name: Moonrock Linen
results.title: New Balance 9060 Moonrock Linen
results.description:
The New Balance 9060 Moonrock Linen takes elements from the 990 and updates this retro silhouette with futuristic design details.

Taking cues from heritage performance running sneakers, the 9060 Moonrock Linen boasts a bulky midsole and a rubber outsole with enhanced traction. The chunky midsole houses New Balances signature ABZORB technology and SBS cushioning, both of which provide responsive cushioning without weighing the foot down. In terms of branding, the New Balance N can be found on the lateral side panel and the tongue houses an embedded triangular tag that reads 9060. Like other 9060 models, this version has a transparent CR device, which wraps around the heel.

Our StockX experts like the Dark Arctic accents on the heel and around the quarter panel because they contrast the sneakers light upper. The New Balance 9060 Moonrock Linen was released on November 30th, 2023, and retailed at $150.

results.name: Bricks & Wood Echoes of a Butterfly
results.title: New Balance 1906U Bricks & Wood Echoes of a Butterfly

results.name: Grey Matter Harbor Grey
results.title: New Balance 530 Grey Matter Harbor Grey
results.description:
The New Balance 530 Grey Matter Harbor Grey is a sneaker inspired by the '90s with modern twists to the classic running shoe.

The New Balance 530 Grey Matter comes with an upper that is primarily mesh. It has leather overlays in a Grey Matter and Harbor Grey colorway that has white and black accents. The shoe features the "N" logo on the quarter panels in Grey Matter with a white outline. Harbor Grey and Grey Matter leather overlays form a cage on the shoe, which uses grey laces for closure. A black heel loop tab contrasts the grey padded collar and features two grey vertical stripes. The shoe also features a "530" logo overlay on the lateral heel in Harbor Grey with white outlining. The outer sole is made of black rubber and contrasts the grey foam midsole.

What do our experts love about the New Balance 530 Grey Matter Harbor Grey? StockX experts like the retro design combined with Abzorb technology in the sole for comfort. The 530 Grey Matter Harbor was released on 1st February 2023 for $100.

results.name: Fuchsia Pink
results.title: New Balance 9060 Fuchsia Pink
results.description:
The New Balance 9060 Fuchsia Pink is a low-top performance shoe designed by James Lee and Yue Wu.

The Fuchsia Pink New Balance 9060 features an upper with a base of Pale Pink mesh for breathability. Suede overlays in a bright Fuchsia color cross the upper to form the toecap, eyestays, mudguard, midfoot, and heel. The New Balance N appears in an off-white color on the lateral side, and again on the inner side in embroidered pink dashed stitching. The white leather heel collar also contains pink NB branding, while the tongue features a 9060 patch. A pink support is seen at the heel, and the shoe sits on a chunky Pale Pink midsole with ABZORB cushioning and brighter pink accents. The outsole is black.

Our favorite thing about this sneaker is the Fuchsia colorway, which is bold and elegant at the same time. The New Balance 9060 Fuchsia Pink was released on August 15, 2024, for $150.

results.name: Sea Salt Black
results.title: New Balance 327 Sea Salt Black
results.description:
The New Balance 327 Sea Salt Black arrives sporting a heritage running silhouette inspired by the '70s.

The New Balance 327 Sea Salt Black is crafted from a breathable, lightweight nylon and suede upper, padded insole, and shock-absorbing rubber sole for unmatched comfort. New Balance's hard-to-miss "N" logo graces the sides in black in addition to the NB hits on the tongue and insoles alike. Finally, its design is rounded off with a midsole lined in a durable black rubber outsole that runs from the top heel to the toe.

The New Balance 327 Sea Salt Black was released in March 2021 and retailed for $90.

results.name: Silver Metallic Sea Salt
results.title: New Balance 1906R Silver Metallic Sea Salt
results.description:
The New Balance 1906R Silver Metallic Sea Salt adds a neutral colorway with metallic accents to the recognizable 1906R silhouette.

Featuring a bulky construction and crisscrossing overlays, the New Balance 1906R Silver Metallic Sea Salt draws inspiration from early 2000s technical running shoes. However, the gentle colorway is a contemporary addition. The base features lightweight mesh in Sea Salt and synthetic leather overlays in Silver Metallic with reflective detailing. The ABZORB midsole and N-ergy cushioning provide stability and protect against impact. In addition, the Stability Web technology creates a supportive base for the runner. The laces come in Sea Salt and can be adjusted for a customizable fit.

Our experts at StockX like the splash of black beneath the heel that breaks up the Sea Salt and tan tones on the midsole. The New Balance 1906R Silver Metallic Sea Salt was released on November 24, 2023, and retailed at $155.

results.name: Protection Pack Black Grey
results.title: New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Black Grey
results.description:
The New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Black Grey comes in a black and gray color palette.

The New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Black Grey has an upper that is constructed from a variety of black and gray materials, including durable mesh and breathable synthetic overlays. The classic "N" emblem appears in contrasting white and black on the sides. The midsole features a white and grey colorway. The ABZORB technology included in the shoe's cushioned midsole provides shock absorption and responsiveness. The shoes black outsole is constructed from long-lasting rubber with a directional tread pattern for superior grip and traction. The lacing system offers a customized fit, while the cushioned tongue and collar provide comfort and stability.

The New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Black Grey was released for a retail price of $170 on March 3rd, 2023.

results.name: Moonbeam
results.title: New Balance 530 Moonbeam
results.description:
The New Balance 530 Moonbeam is a retro running shoe that works just as well as a lifestyle shoe. This sneaker features Y2K-era tech details and a chunky, vintage feel with every stride.

This low-top running sneaker in an understated, subtle colorway begins with an upper of creamy Moonbeam-colored lightweight, breathable mesh as its base. Tonal leather overlays circle across the upper, layering over each other. Perforations at the toe cap and side panel help enhance the comfort afforded by breathability. Tonal rope laces cross over a cream-colored mesh tongue for a secure fit. A beige pull tab at the heel with cream-colored stripes helps ease on and off this pair of kicks. An ABZORB midsole in different shades of cream provides springy cushioning, while a cream-colored and tan rubber outsole offers flexible grip and impact absorption.

Our favorite aspect of this elegant, monochromatic shoe is the subtle 530 branding that courses across an overlay at the lateral collar, thus locking in the classic look. The New Balance 530 Moonbeam was released on April 12, 2021, for $95 retail.

results.name: Off White
results.title: New Balance 2002R Off White
results.description:
The New Balance 2002R Off White is a running shoe that comes in a Beige Off White colorway.

This sneaker features an upper constructed with mesh, leather and suede with grey tones around the collar. Other details include jersey lining, a padded tongue and collar, the "N" logo on the sides, and the "2002R" on the lateral just below the collar. Rounding out the design is a textured ACTEVA LITE rubber midsole that utilizes the ABZORB cushioning technology and a black treaded N-ergy rubber outsole.

The New Balance 2002R Off White was released on September 2nd, 2022, retailing at $120.

results.name: Ivory
results.title: New Balance 530 Ivory
results.description:
Since its launch in 1992, New Balance 530 Ivory has become a popular unisex sneaker due to its performance running shoe design.

New Balance 530 Ivory's upper is made of synthetic leather, while the midsole is produced through a cold cement process. New Balance 530 Ivory's design is ivory, white, and black, with a style code of MR530SH. The sneaker weighs 339 grams (12 oz.) and features a lace-up closure. New Balance 530 Ivory also features the New Balance "N" logo on its quarter panel.

New Balance 530 Ivory became available on July 5, 2022, at a retail price of $80.

results.name: Silver Black
results.title: New Balance 1906R Silver Black
results.description:
The New Balance 1906R Silver Black leans into Y2K trends with a striking colorway of metallic silver, black, and white.

Featuring a low-top, lace-up design inspired by sneakers from the early 2000s, this version of the 1906R boasts a white mesh base with black accents on the heel, sock liner, rubber outsole, and ribbons threading through the signature New Balance N logo. However, the shiny silver overlays crisscrossing the upper stand out the most. The ABZORB SBS heel increases stability, while the ABZORB midsole protects against impact stress. Finally, the N-ergy technology in the outsole adds superior shock absorption as the Stability Web supports the midfoot arch.

Our experts at StockX like the classic New Balance 1906R branding, including "1906R" on the overlays, "NB RUNNING" on the tongue, and "NB" on the heel. The New Balance 1906R Silver Black was released on June 1, 2024, and sold for $155.

results.name: Munsell White
results.title: New Balance 530 Munsell White
results.description:
The New Balance 530 Munsell White arrives in a Munsell white and silver metallic colorway.

The New Balance 530 Munsell White has an upper that is crafted from a blend of leather and synthetic materials, making it both durable and lightweight. The shoe features ABZORB cushioning in the midsole for reduced impact. The outsole is constructed from sturdy rubber, making it both grippy and stable. The shoe features "N" branding on the lateral sides and an "NB" logo on the tongue.

The New Balance 530 Munsell White was made available on December 8th, 2020, and sold for a retail price of $100.

results.name: Olivine
results.title: New Balance 9060 Olivine
results.description:
The New Balance 9060 Olivine is a sneaker that pays homage to the design of the 99X model with several modern and futuristic updates.

This iteration of the New Balance 9060 is made with a high-quality leather and breathable mesh upper. Light olive green mesh forms the base of the upper, while leather and synthetic overlays adorn the midsole, toe, and heel in different shades of green. The New Balance "N" logo appears on the midsoles under the laces, with one of them being solid white outlined in green and the other being made up of white dashes. The heel collar is a dark olive green and displays the "NB" logo, while the "NB 9060" logo appears on the tongue. The durable rubber outsole provides excellent grip, while the sole is cushioned with ABZORB cushioning.

Our favorite feature of this shoe is the muted green colorway. This allows the shoe to exude style and functionality in a subtle way. The New Balance 9060 Olivine was released on March 30, 2024, for a retail price of $160.

results.name: Triple White
results.title: New Balance 9060 Triple White
results.description:
The New Balance 9060 Triple White takes the classic 9060 silhouette and adds an all-white colorway. Including white on the upper, outsole, midsole, and lining allows the sneakers design elements to stand out.

This version of the 9060 finds inspiration in the 990 and the 860, giving the lifestyle shoe an early 2000s aesthetic. It features wavy leather overlays on the upper that complement the wavy pattern on the thick midsole. The upper is made of breathable mesh, while the heel displays a transparent CR device. This feature can be found on other 9060 models and supports heel stability. Although the curving logo on the tongue resembles the lace jewel on the 991, the diamond-like pattern of the outsole finds inspiration in the 860.

Our StockX experts like how ABZORB cushioning and pods in the midsole contribute to the sneakers chunky appearance. The New Balance 9060 Triple White was released on January 12th, 2024, and retailed at $150.

results.name: Mushroom Timberwolf
results.title: New Balance 9060 Mushroom Timberwolf
results.description:
The New Balance 9060 Mushroom Timberwolf puts a futuristic spin on classic New Balance designs, including the 99X, the 991, and the 860.

The Mushroom Timberwolf colorway of the New Balance 960 sports an upper of lightweight and breathable white mesh with pig suede overlays in complementary shades of gray, tan, and brown. The classic side panel N logo is constructed from pale embroidered dashed lines that match the cream-colored shoelaces. The heel features a semi-translucent CR device as well as NB branding. The sock liner is cream-colored and the black insole and gray tongue each sport New Balance branding. The outsole is black rubber with a red diamond traction pattern.

What we love most about this sneaker is the high-performance sole unit. The midsole is constructed of ABZORB in an exaggerated wavy pattern with ABZORB SBS in the heel for cushioning and impact absorption. The New Balance 9060 Mushroom Timberwolf was released on September 22, 2023, for a retail price of $150.

results.name: Steel Grey
results.title: New Balance 530 Steel Grey
results.description:
The New Balance 530 was originally released in 1992, and the New Balance 530 in Steel Grey is a recreation of the companys classic running shoe designs.

The New Balance 530 Steel Grey boasts of a synthetic mesh upper construction with steel grey leather overlays appearing on most of the upper. The signature N logo appears in white, and the white continues to the laces and the chunky ENCAP midsole and ABZORB heel cushioning. The adjustable lace closure provides a comfortable fit, and the ABZORB heel cushioning provides comfort.

The New Balance 530 Steel Grey was released in January 2021 and originally retailed for $110.

results.name: Protection Pack Dark Moss
results.title: New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Dark Moss
results.description:
The New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Dark Moss is one of four colorways in the Protection Pack.

Taking inspiration from New Balances MR2002 high-end running shoe from 2010, this silhouette is dressed in dark moss, grey, and black while sporting a peek of yellow coming from the back heel. Its innovative ripstop base layer is eye-catching and functional as it is waterproof. Comfort is top of mind as an ABZORB midsole and ABZORB SBS heel provides cushioning with every step. Branding hits can be found on the sides, top, and bottom of the tongue. Giving off an earthy autumn vibe, these sneakers come with toggle laces.

Our experts think that the tech features in this shoe are what make it stand out. The Stability Web in the outsole provides arch support while a proprietary N-ergy outsole absorbs all shocks. The New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Dark Moss debuted on September 21, 2023, and sold at a retail price of $160.
